    "text": "The sterile lines 521A and 170A, and the restorer lines Ji318R and 0-30 were promising parents with high general combining ability. All endogenous substances of root bleeding sap were positively correlated with the sum of parental general combining ability at highly significant levels. IAA, CTK, GA3, ABA, soluble sugar, amino acid, and root bleeding intensity were positively correlated with male general combining ability at significant or highly significant levels.",
